The first seasonal snow captured from space.

This@CopernicusEU #Sentinel2 image from 21 November 2024 captures the first snow of the season over Denmark and southern Sweden.

Zoom in to explore this image at its full 10 m resolution  https://t.co/HTdiSZbgaN
